## Introduction

This is a simple Markdown file  with a header inclusion on top and some abbreviations which are used from the YAML header.

They can be used like this:

```
This document was modified at {date} by {author}, {UP}.
```

The output is:

This document was modified at {date} by {author}, {UP}.

